{
  "name": "01 — Recipe Chat Agent",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Recipe Chat Agent\n**Goal:** Conversational agent that finds and adapts recipes for families with kids.\n\n**Tools:**\n- **Recipe Search** (TheMealDB) — common dishes in English\n- **Google Search** (SerpAPI) — regional or specific dishes\n\n**How to use:** Click **Chat** and ask for a recipe. The agent will ask for kid ages and allergies before transforming.\n\n**Logging:** Every interaction is logged to Google Sheets (session, input, output, tools used).",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 700,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000001",
      "name": "NOTE — Recipe Chat Agent",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-760, -400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Google Sheets Setup\n\n1. Create a Google Sheet with these column headers (row 1):\n   `session_id` | `timestamp` | `input` | `output` | `tools_used`\n2. Add a **Google Sheets** credential in n8n (Settings → Credentials)\n3. Paste the Sheet URL in the **Log to Google Sheets** node\n\n⚠️ `tools_used` is **self-reported** by the agent — it may be inaccurate. Good teaching moment about observability limitations.",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000011",
      "name": "NOTE — Google Sheets Setup",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-60, -400]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "public": true,
        "mode": "webhook",
        "options": {
          "responseMode": "lastNode"
        }
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000002",
      "name": "When chat message received",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.chatTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [-760, -100],
      "webhookId": "bb000001-webhook-0001"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "={{ $json.chatInput }}",
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a friendly recipe assistant for families with kids.\n\n## What you do\nHelp users find and adapt recipes for children.\n\n## Information you need\nBefore transforming any recipe, collect:\n1. Kid ages (required — ask if missing)\n2. Allergies or dislikes (ask once, optional)\n\n## How you work\n- If the user gives a common dish name (chicken, pasta, lasagna...), use Recipe Search (TheMealDB)\n- If TheMealDB returns no results, or the dish is regional/specific (croquetas, tortilla de patatas, pad thai), use Google Search\n- If the user pastes a full recipe, use it directly — no need to search\n- Once you have the recipe + kid ages, transform it:\n  1. Simplify for beginners\n  2. Adapt for kids (fun names, safety notes, age-appropriate portions)\n  3. Generate a shopping list with estimated cost\n- After presenting the result, ask if they want changes\n\n## Rules\n- Always ask for kid ages before transforming\n- Never invent recipes — search or ask the user to paste one\n- Recipe Search terms must be in English and simple (e.g. 'chicken', 'lasagna')\n- Be conversational, not robotic\n\n## Logging\nAt the end of every response, add on a new line:\n---\nTools used: [list each tool you called in order, comma-separated, or \"none\"]"
        }
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000003",
      "name": "Recipe Chat Agent",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [-420, -100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "bb000001-assign-0010",
              "name": "session_id",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "={{ $('When chat message received').first().json.sessionId }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "bb000001-assign-0011",
              "name": "timestamp",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "={{ $now.toFormat('yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "bb000001-assign-0012",
              "name": "input",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "={{ $('When chat message received').first().json.chatInput }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "bb000001-assign-0013",
              "name": "output",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "={{ $json.output.split('\\n---')[0].trim() }}"
            },
            {
              "id": "bb000001-assign-0014",
              "name": "tools_used",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "={{ $json.output.includes('Tools used:') ? $json.output.split('Tools used:').pop().trim() : 'unknown' }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000009",
      "name": "Prepare Log",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [-100, -100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "append",
        "documentId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "url",
          "value": "YOUR_GOOGLE_SHEET_URL"
        },
        "sheetName": {
          "__rl": true,
          "mode": "list",
          "value": "Sheet1",
          "cachedResultName": "Sheet1"
        },
        "columns": {
          "mappingMode": "autoMapInputData"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000010",
      "name": "Log to Google Sheets",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets",
      "typeVersion": 4.5,
      "position": [160, -100],
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "bb000001-assign-0001",
              "name": "output",
              "type": "string",
              "value": "={{ $json.output }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000004",
      "name": "Output",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [420, -100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "openai/gpt-4o-mini",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000005",
      "name": "OpenRouter Chat Model",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatOpenRouter",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-620, 140]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "contextWindowLength": 10,
        "sessionIdType": "customKey",
        "sessionKey": "={{ $json.sessionId }}"
      },
      "id": "bb000001-0001-4000-b000-000000000006",
